#. Tag: date
#: index.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "2016-06-23"
msgstr "23.06.2016"

#. Tag: releaseinfo
#: index.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plasma 5.8"
msgstr "Plasma 5.8"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:23 index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can customize window settings specifically only for some windows."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko prilagodite okenske nastavitve posamezno za samo nekatera okna."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "KControl"
msgstr "KControl"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "window settings"
msgstr "okenske nastavitve"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid "window placement"
msgstr "postavitev oken"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "window size"
msgstr "velikost oken"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window Specific Settings: Quick Start"
msgstr "Nastavitve za posamezna okna: Hitri začetek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that this configuration will not take effect if you do not use "
"&kwin; as your window manager. If you do use a different window manager, "
"please refer to its documentation for how to customize window behavior."
msgstr ""
"Vedite, da vse nastavitve v tem modulu ne bodo učinkovale, če ne boste "
"uporabljali &kwin; kot okenskega upravitelja. Če uporabljate drugega "
"okenskega upravitelja, prosim preverite njegovo dokumentacijo glede "
"prilagajanja obnašanja oken."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many of the settings you can configure here are those you can configure on a "
"global basis in the <guilabel>Window Behavior</guilabel> &systemsettings; "
"module, however some of them are even more detailed."
msgstr ""
"Večino nastavitev, ki jih nastavite tukaj, lahko v splošnem nastavite v "
"modulu  <guilabel>Obnašanje oken</guilabel>, vendar so nekatere tukaj bolj "
"podrobne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"They encompass geometry, placement, whether a window should be kept above or "
"below others, focus stealing prevention, and translucency settings."
msgstr ""
"Vključujejo geometrijo, postavitev, ali naj bo okno nad ali pod vsemi, "
"ravnanje s fokusiranjem in nastavitve prosojnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can access this module in two ways: from the titlebar of the application "
"you wish to configure, or from the &systemsettings;. If you start it from "
"within &systemsettings; you can use the <guibutton>New...</guibutton> to "
"create a window profile, and the <guibutton>Detect Window Properties</"
"guibutton> button on the resulting dialog to partially fill in the required "
"information for the application you wish to configure."
msgstr ""
"Do tega modula lahko dostopate na dva načina: iz naslovne vrstice "
"aplikacije, ki jo želite konfigurirati, ali iz &systemsettings;. Če ga "
"zaženete znotraj &systemsettings; lahko uporabite <guibutton>Novo ...</"
"guibutton>, da ustvarite profil okna, in nato gumb <guibutton>Zaznaj "
"lastnosti okna</guibutton> v pogovornem oknu, ki se odpre, kjer delno "
"izpolnite zahtevane informacije za aplikacijo, ki jo želite konfigurirati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also at any time <guibutton>Modify...</guibutton> or "
"<guibutton>Delete</guibutton> any stored settings profile, and reorder the "
"list. Reordering the list using the <guibutton>Move Up</guibutton> and "
"<guibutton>Move Down</guibutton> buttons effects on how they are applied."
msgstr ""
"Kadarkoli lahko tudi uporabite gumba <guibutton>Spremeni ...</guibutton> ali "
"<guibutton>Zbriši</guibutton> za spreminjanje shranjenih nastavitvenih "
"profilov ali pa spremenite vrstni red v seznamu. Prerazporeditev seznama z "
"gumboma <guibutton>Premakni gor</guibutton> in <guibutton>Premakni navzdol</"
"guibutton> vpliva na uporabo standardnih nastavitvenih profilov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Pregled"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwin; allows the end-user to define rules to alter an application's window "
"attributes."
msgstr ""
"&kwin; omogoča končnemu uporabniku, da definira pravila spreminjanja "
"atributov okna aplikacije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, when an application is started, it can be forced to always run "
"on <emphasis>Virtual Desktop 2</emphasis>. Or a defect in an application can "
"be worked-around to force the window above others."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, ko se aplikacija zažene, jo je mogoče prisiliti, da se vedno "
"izvaja na <emphasis>Virtualnem namizju 2</emphasis>. Lahko pa se uporabi za "
"odpravo napake v aplikaciji, da se okno vseeno prikaže nad drugimi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Step-by-step <link linkend=\"examples\">examples</link> are provided along "
"with detailed information on using the <link linkend=\"kwin-rule-editor"
"\">&kwin; Rule Editor</link> to specify <link linkend=\"window-matching"
"\">Window Matching</link> and <link linkend=\"window-attributes\">Window "
"Attributes</link>."
msgstr ""
"Na voljo so <link linkend=\"examples\">primeri</link> po korakih skupaj s "
"podrobnimi informacijami o uporabi <link linkend=\"kwin-rule-editor\">&kwin; "
"Urejevalnik pravil</link> za določitev <link linkend=\"window-matching"
"\">Ujemanja oken</link> in <link linkend=\"window-attributes\">Atributov "
"oken</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples and Application Workaround"
msgstr "Primeri in Obhod uporabe (Application Workaround)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To see what's possible, detailed <link linkend=\"examples\">examples</link> "
"are provided which can also be used to model your own rules."
msgstr ""
"Če želite videti, kaj je mogoče, so na voljo podrobni <link linkend="
"\"examples\">primeri</link>, ki jih lahko uporabite tudi za modeliranje "
"lastnih pravil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A special page is dedicated to address <link linkend=\"application-"
"workarounds\">Application Workaround</link>."
msgstr ""
"Posebna stran je namenjena obravnavi <link linkend=\"application-workarounds"
"\">Rešitve z obhodom aplikacije</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "KWin Rule Editor"
msgstr "KWin Urejevalnik pravil"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Invoking the KWin Rule Editor"
msgstr "Priklic urejevalnika pravil KWin"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are several ways to invoke the &kwin; Rule Editor. Below are two:"
msgstr ""
"Obstaja več načinov za priklic &kwin; Urejevalnika pravil. Spodaj sta dve:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right-click on the title-bar of any window, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>More "
"Actions</guimenu><guimenuitem>Window Manager Settings...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> and in the <guilabel>Configure</guilabel> window, select "
"<guilabel>Window Rules</guilabel> or"
msgstr ""
"Z desno tipko miške kliknite naslovno vrstico katerega koli okna, izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Več dejanj</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavitve upravitelja "
"oken ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in v oknu <guilabel>Konfiguriraj</"
"guilabel>, izberite <guilabel>Pravila oken</guilabel> ali"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>System Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Window Behavior</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Window Rules</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sistemske nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Vedenje oken</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Pravila za okna</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main window is used to:"
msgstr "Glavno okno se uporablja za:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Affect rules with <guilabel>New...</guilabel>, <guilabel>Modify...</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Delete</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Vplivajte na pravila z <guilabel>Novo ...</guilabel>, <guilabel>Spremeni ..."
"</guilabel> in <guilabel>Izbriši</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Share rules with others via <guilabel>Import</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Export</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Delite pravila z drugimi prek <guilabel>Uvozi</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Izvozi</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ensure desired <link linkend=\"rule-evaluation\">rule evaluation</link> "
"using <guilabel>Move Up</guilabel> and <guilabel>Move Down</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Zagotovite želeno <link linkend=\"rule-evaluation\">vrednotenje pravila</"
"link> z uporabo <guilabel>Premakni gor</guilabel> in <guilabel>Premakni "
"navzdol</guilabel>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rule Evaluation"
msgstr "Vrednotenje pravil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When an application starts (or the rules are modified), &kwin; evaluates the "
"rules from the top of the list to the bottom. For all rules which match a "
"window, the collective set of attributes are applied to the window, then the "
"window is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Ko se aplikacija zažene (ali se pravila spremenijo), &kwin; ovrednoti "
"pravila od začetka do konca seznama. Za vsa pravila, ki se ujemajo z oknom, "
"se skupni niz atributov uporabi za okno, nato pa se okno prikaže."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Should two or more matching rules enable the same attribute, the setting in "
"the <emphasis>first</emphasis> rule in the list is used."
msgstr ""
"Če dve ali več ujemajočih se pravil omogočita isti atribut, se uporabi "
"nastavitev v <emphasis>prvem</emphasis> pravilu na seznamu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can tailor children windows for the application by placing the more "
"restrictive rules first - see the <link linkend=\"application-on-all-"
"desktops-and-handle-one-child-window-uniquely\">Kopete and Kopete Chat "
"Window</link> example."
msgstr ""
"Otroška okna za aplikacijo lahko prilagodite tako, da najprej postavite bolj "
"restriktivna pravila - glejte <link linkend=\"application-on-all-desktops-"
"and-handle-one-child-window-uniquely\">Kopete in Kopete okno za klepet </"
"link> primer."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rule Editor"
msgstr "Urejevalnik pravil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "The editor is composed of four tabs:"
msgstr "Urejevalnik je sestavljen iz štirih zavihkov:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window matching"
msgstr "Ujemanje oken"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:143 index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Size &amp; Position</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Velikost &amp; Položaj</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:144 index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Arrangement &amp; Access</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel> Položaj &amp; Dostop </guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:145 index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Appearance &amp; Fixes</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Videz &amp; Popravki </guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As the name implies, <guilabel>Window matching</guilabel> is used to specify "
"criteria to match one or more windows. The other three tabs are used to "
"alter the attributes of the matching windows."
msgstr ""
"Kot pove ime, se <guilabel>Ujemanje oken</guilabel> uporablja za podajanje "
"kriterijev za ujemanje enega ali več oken. Ostali trije zavihki se "
"uporabljajo za spreminjanje atributov ustreznih oken."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "Panels can also be affected."
msgstr "To lahko vpliva tudi na plošče."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:151 index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window Matching"
msgstr "Ujemanje oken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each window rule has user specified <link linkend=\"window-matching\">Window "
"Matching</link> criteria. &kwin; uses the criteria to determine whether the "
"rule is applicable for an application."
msgstr ""
"Vsako pravilo za okno veljajo določena merila <link linkend=\"window-matching"
"\">Ujemanje oken</link>. &kwin; uporablja merila za ugotavljanje, ali je "
"pravilo uporabno za aplikacijo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:155 index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window Attributes"
msgstr "Značilnosti oken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Along with Window Matching criteria, each window rule has a set of <link "
"linkend=\"window-attributes\">Window Attributes</link>. The attributes "
"override the corresponding application's settings and are applied before the "
"window is displayed by &kwin;."
msgstr ""
"Poleg meril za ujemanje oken ima vsako pravilo za okno nabor <link linkend="
"\"window-attributes\">lastnosti oken</link>. Lastnosti preglasijo nastavitve "
"ustrezne aplikacije in se uporabijo, preden &kwin; prikaže okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Window Matching</guilabel> tab is used to specify the criteria "
"&kwin; uses to evaluate whether the rule is applicable for a given window."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Ujemanje oken</guilabel> se uporablja za določanje "
"kriterijev, ki jih &kwin; uporablja za oceno, ali je pravilo uporabno za "
"dano okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zero (match any window) or more of the following may be specified:"
msgstr ""
"Nastavi se lahko nič (okno se ujema s katerim koli oknom) ali kaj od "
"naslednjega:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Window class (application)</guilabel> - match the class."
msgstr "<guilabel>Razred okna (aplikacija)</guilabel> - ujemanje z razredom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Match whole window class</guilabel> - include matching the "
"secondary class."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ujemanje celotnega razreda okna</guilabel> - vključi ujemanje "
"sekundarnega razreda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Window role</guilabel> - restrict the match to the function of the "
"window (&eg; a <emphasis>main window</emphasis>, a <emphasis>chat window</"
"emphasis>, &etc;)"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vloga okna</guilabel> - omeji ujemanje na funkcijo okna (&eg;. "
"<emphasis>glavno okno</emphasis>, <emphasis>okno za klepet</emphasis>, &etc;)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Window types</guilabel> - restrict the match to the type of "
"window: <guilabel>Normal Window</guilabel>, <guilabel>Dialog Window</"
"guilabel>, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vrste oken</guilabel> - omejite ujemanje na vrsto okna: "
"<guilabel>Običajno okno</guilabel>, <guilabel>Pogovorno okno</guilabel> itd.;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Window title</guilabel> - restrict the match to the title of the "
"window."
msgstr "<guilabel>Naslov okna</guilabel> - omeji ujemanje na naslov okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Machine (hostname)</guilabel> - restrict the match to the host "
"name associated with the window."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Naprava (ime gostitelja)</guilabel> - omeji ujemanje na ime "
"gostitelja, povezano z oknom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While it's possible to manually enter the above information, the preferred "
"method is to use the <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> button."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav je mogoče ročno vnesti zgornje informacije, je prednostna metoda "
"uporaba gumba <guilabel>Zaznaj lastnosti okna</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each field, the following operators can be applied against the field "
"value:"
msgstr ""
"Za vsako polje lahko v odnosu z vrednostjo polja uporabite naslednje "
"operatorje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Unimportant</guilabel> - ignore the field."
msgstr "<guilabel>Nepomembno</guilabel> - prezri polje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exact Match"
msgstr "Natančno ujemanje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Substring Match"
msgstr "Ujemanje podniza"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Both <guilabel>Exact Match</guilabel> and <guilabel>Substring Match</"
"guilabel> implement case insensitive matching. For example, <emphasis>AB</"
"emphasis> matches the string <emphasis>AB</emphasis>, <emphasis>ab</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>Ab</emphasis> and <emphasis>aB</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Tako <guilabel>Natančno ujemanje</guilabel> kot <guilabel>Ujemanje podniza</"
"guilabel> izvajata ujemanje brez razlikovanja med velikimi in malimi črkami. "
"Na primer, <emphasis>AB</emphasis> se ujema z nizi<emphasis>AB</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>ab</emphasis>, <emphasis>Ab</emphasis> in <emphasis>aB</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Regular Expression</guilabel> - Qt's regular expressions are "
"implemented - see <ulink url=\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qregexp.html\">pattern "
"matching using regular expressions</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Regularni izraz</guilabel> - implementirani so regularni izrazi Qt "
"- glejte <ulink url=\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qregexp.html\">ujemanje vzorcev "
"z uporabo regularnih izrazov</ulink> ."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Detect Window Properties"
msgstr "Zaznaj lastnosti oken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> function simplifies the "
"process of entering the matching-criteria."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija <guilabel>Zaznaj lastnosti okna</guilabel> poenostavi postopek "
"vnosa kriterijev ujemanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "For the application you'd like to create a rule, start the application."
msgstr "Zaženite aplikacijo, za katero želite ustvariti pravilo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next, in the <guilabel>Window matching</guilabel> tab, set the number of "
"seconds of delay before the <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> "
"function starts. The default is zero seconds."
msgstr ""
"Nato na zavihku <guilabel>Ujemanje oken</guilabel> nastavite število sekund "
"zakasnitve, preden se zažene funkcija <guilabel>Zaznaj lastnosti okna</"
"guilabel>. Privzeta vrednost je nič sekund."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click on <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> and"
msgstr "Kliknite <guilabel>Zaznaj lastnosti okna</guilabel> in"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the mouse-cursor turns to cross-hairs, place it inside the application "
"window (not the title bar) and left-click."
msgstr ""
"Ko se miškin kazalec spremeni v križec, ga postavite v okno aplikacije (ne v "
"naslovno vrstico) in kliknite z levo tipko miške."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A new window is presented with information about the selected window. Select "
"the desired fields:"
msgstr ""
"Prikaže se novo okno z informacijami o izbranem oknu. Izberite želena polja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Secondary class name</guilabel> - some applications have a "
"secondary class name. This value can be used to restrict windows by this "
"value."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ime sekundarnega razreda</guilabel> - nekatere aplikacije imajo "
"ime sekundarnega razreda. To vrednost lahko uporabite za omejitev oken, ki "
"jo zavzemajo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window role"
msgstr "Vloga okna"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Window type</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Tip okna</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window title"
msgstr "Naslov okna"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <guilabel>OK</guilabel> button to back-fill the <guilabel>Window "
"Matching</guilabel> criteria."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb <guilabel>V redu</guilabel>, da ponovno zapolnite kriterij "
"<guilabel>Ujemanje oken</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By using a combination of the information, a rule can apply to an entire "
"application (by <guilabel>Class</guilabel>) or a to a specific window "
"<guilabel>Type</guilabel> within the <guilabel>Class</guilabel> - say a "
"<guilabel>Toolbar</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo kombinacije informacij lahko pravilo velja za celotno aplikacijo "
"(po <guilabel>Razredu</guilabel>) ali za določen  <guilabel>Tip</guilabel> "
"okna znotraj <guilabel>Razreda</guilabel> > - recimo <guilabel>Orodno "
"vrstico</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid "The attributes which can be set are grouped by function in three tabs:"
msgstr ""
"Atributi, ki jih je mogoče nastaviti, so razvrščeni po funkcijah v treh "
"zavihkih:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each attribute has a set of parameters which determines its disposition."
msgstr "Vsak atribut ima nabor parametrov, ki določajo njegovo razporeditev."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "Parametri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each attribute, minimally, accepts one of the following parameters. "
"Additional, attribute-specific arguments are listed within each <link "
"linkend=\"attributes\">attribute</link> definition."
msgstr ""
"Vsak atribut sprejme najmanj enega od naslednjih parametrov. Dodatni "
"argumenti, specifični za atribute, so navedeni znotraj vsake definicije "
"<link linkend=\"attributes\">atributa</link>."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do Not Affect"
msgstr "Ne vplivaj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ensure a subsequent rule, which matches the window, does not affect the "
"attribute."
msgstr ""
"Zagotovite, da naslednje pravilo, ki se ujema z oknom, ne vpliva na atribut."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "Apply Initially"
msgstr "Prijavite se na začetku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start the window with the attribute and allow it to be changed at run-time."
msgstr "Zaženite okno z atributom in dovolite, da se spremeni med izvajanjem."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remember"
msgstr "Zapomni si"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the attribute setting as defined in the rule and if changed at run-time, "
"save and use the new value instead."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite nastavitev atributa, kot je definirana v pravilu, in če jo "
"spremenite med izvajanjem, shranite in namesto tega uporabite novo vrednost."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Force"
msgstr "Prisila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid "The setting cannot be changed at run-time."
msgstr "Nastavitev ni mogoče spremeniti med izvajanjem."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Apply Now, Force Temporarily"
msgstr "Prijavite se zdaj, vsilite začasno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apply/Force the setting once and unset the attribute.The difference between "
"the two is at run-time, <guilabel>Apply Now</guilabel> allows the attribute "
"to be changed and <guilabel>Force Temporarily</guilabel> prohibits it to be "
"altered until all affected windows exit."
msgstr ""
"Enkrat uporabite/vsilite nastavitev in razveljavite atribut. Razlika med "
"obema je v času izvajanja, <guilabel>Uporabi zdaj</guilabel> dovoljuje "
"spreminjanje atributa, <guilabel>Začasno vsili</guilabel> pa prepoveduje "
"spreminjati, dokler ne zapustijo vsa okna, na katere ima nastavitev vpliv."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For <guilabel>Apply Now</guilabel>, if the rule has no other attributes set, "
"the rule is deleted after evaluation whereas <guilabel>Force Temporarily</"
"guilabel>, the rule is deleted after the last affected window terminates."
msgstr ""
"Za <guilabel>Uporabi zdaj</guilabel>, če pravilo nima nastavljenih drugih "
"atributov, se pravilo izbriše po ovrednotenju, medtem ko se pri "
"<guilabel>Začasno vsili</guilabel> pravilo izbriše, ko se konča zadnje okno, "
"za katerega veljajo te nastvitve."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid "Attributes"
msgstr "Lastnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> button back-fills "
"attribute-specific values - for more information see <link linkend=\"window-"
"matching\">Window Matching</link>. For example the height and width values "
"of the <guilabel>Size</guilabel> attribute is set to the height and width of "
"the detected window."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guilabel>Zaznaj lastnosti okna</guilabel> zapolni vrednosti, "
"specifične za lastnost - za več informacij glejte <link linkend=\"window-"
"matching\">Ujemanje oken</link>. Vrednosti višine in širine lastnosti "
"<guilabel>Velikost</guilabel> so na primer nastavljene na višino in širino "
"zaznanega okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Yes/No</guilabel> arguments are used to toggle on or off "
"attributes. Leniency with grammar helps one understand how a setting will be "
"processed. <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Face-smile."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> For example, the "
"attribute <guilabel>Skip taskbar</guilabel>, when set to <guilabel>No</"
"guilabel> means do not skip the taskbar. In other words, show the window in "
"the taskbar."
msgstr ""
"Argumenta <guilabel>Da/Ne</guilabel> se uporabljata za vklop ali izklop "
"lastnosti. Prizanesljivost s slovnico pomaga razumeti, kako bo nastavitev "
"obdelana. <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Face-smile."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> Na primer, "
"lastnost <guilabel>Preskoči opravilno vrstico</guilabel>, ko je nastavljena "
"na <guilabel>Ne</guilabel> pomeni, da ne preskoči opravilne vrstice. Z "
"drugimi besedami, pomeni pokaži okno v opravilni vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Size &amp; Position</title>"
msgstr "<title>Velikost &amp; Položaj</title>"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Position"
msgstr "Pozicija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Position the window's upper left corner at the specified x,y coordinate."
msgstr "Postavite zgornji levi kot okna na določeno koordinato x,y."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kwin;'s origin, (0,0), is the upper left of the desktop."
msgstr "Izvor &kwin;, (0,0), je zgornji levi del namizja."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "Size"
msgstr "Velikost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "The width and height of the window."
msgstr "Širina in višina okna."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maximized horizontally, Maximized vertically"
msgstr "Maksimirano vodoravno, maksimirano navpično"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These attributes are used to toggle the maximum horizontal/minimum "
"horizontal window attribute."
msgstr ""
"Ti atributi se uporabljajo za preklop največjega vodoravnega/najmanjšega "
"vodoravnega atributa okna."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Desktop, Activity, Screen"
msgstr "Namizje, dejavnost, zaslon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Place the window on the specified <emphasis>(Virtual) Desktop</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>Activity</emphasis> or <emphasis>Screen</emphasis>. Use "
"<guilabel>All Desktops</guilabel> to place the window on all "
"<emphasis>Virtual Desktops</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Postavite okno na določeno <emphasis>(virtualno) namizje</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>Dejavnost</emphasis> ali <emphasis>Zaslon</emphasis>. Uporabite "
"<guilabel>Vsa namizja</guilabel>, da postavite okno na vsa "
"<emphasis>Navidezna namizja</emphasis>."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fullscreen, Minimized, Shaded"
msgstr "Celozaslonsko, minimizirano, zasenčeno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle the Fullscreen, Minimize and Shading window attribute. For example, a "
"window can be started Minimized or if it is started Minimized, it can be "
"forced to not."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite med atributi Celozaslonski način, Minimiziraj in Senčenje okna. "
"Na primer, okno je mogoče zagnati pomanjšano ali, če je zagnano pomanjšano, "
"ga je mogoče prisilno zavrniti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Maximized attribute is emulated by using both <guilabel>Maximized "
"horizontally</guilabel> and <guilabel>Maximized vertically</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Initial placement</guilabel> with the <guilabel>Maximizing</"
"guilabel> argument."
msgstr ""
"Maksimiran atribut je posneman z uporabo obeh <guilabel>Maksimizirano "
"vodoravno</guilabel> in <guilabel>Maksimizirano navpično</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>Začetne postavitve</guilabel> z argumentom "
"<guilabel>Maksimiziranje</guilabel>."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid "Initial placement"
msgstr "Začetna postavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Override the global window placement strategy with one of the following:"
msgstr "Preglasite globalno strategijo postavitve oken z enim od naslednjega:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Default</guilabel> - use the global window placement strategy."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Privzeto</guilabel> - uporabite globalno strategijo postavitve "
"oken."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>No Placement</guilabel> - top-left corner."
msgstr "<guilabel>Brez umestitve</guilabel> - zgornji levi kot."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Minimal Overlapping</guilabel> - place where no other window "
"exists."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Minimalno prekrivanje</guilabel> - mesto, kjer ni nobenega drugega "
"okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Maximized</guilabel> - start the window maximized."
msgstr "<guilabel>Povečano</guilabel> - zaženi okno povečano."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Centered</guilabel> - center of the desktop."
msgstr "<guilabel>Na sredini</guilabel> - sredina namizja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid "Random"
msgstr "Naključno"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "In Top-Left Corner"
msgstr "V zgornjem levem kotu"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "Under Mouse"
msgstr "Pod miško"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>On Main Window</guilabel> - restrict placement of a child window "
"to the boundaries of the parent window."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>V glavnem oknu</guilabel> - omeji postavitev podrejenega okna na "
"meje nadrejenega okna."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore requested geometry"
msgstr "Ignoriraj zahtevano geometrijo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle whether to accept or ignore the window's requested geometry position. "
"To avoid conflicts between the default placement strategy and the window's "
"request, the placement strategy is ignored when the window's request is "
"accepted."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite, ali želite sprejeti ali prezreti zahtevani geometrijski položaj "
"okna. Da bi se izognili konfliktom med privzeto strategijo postavitve in "
"zahtevo okna, je strategija postavitve prezrta, ko je zahteva okna sprejeta."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "Minimum size, Maximum size"
msgstr "Najmanjša velikost, največja velikost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid "The minimum and maximum size allowed for the window."
msgstr "Najmanjša in največja dovoljena velikost okna."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Obey geometry restrictions"
msgstr "Upoštevajte geometrijske omejitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle whether to adhere to the window's requested aspect ratio or "
"<emphasis>base increment</emphasis>.In order to understand this attribute, "
"some background is required. Briefly, windows must request from the Window "
"Manager, a base increment: the minimum number of <emphasis>height</emphasis> "
"X <emphasis>width</emphasis> pixels per re-size request. Typically, it's "
"1x1. Other windows though, for example terminal emulators or editors, use "
"fixed-fonts and request their base-increment according to the size of one "
"character."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite, ali želite upoštevati zahtevano razmerje stranic okna ali "
"<emphasis>osnovni prirastek (base increment)</emphasis>. Za razumevanje te "
"lastnosti je potrebno nekaj ozadja. Na kratko, okna morajo od upravitelja "
"oken zahtevati osnovno povečanje: najmanjše število slikovnih pik "
"<emphasis>višine</emphasis> X najmanjše število slikovnih pik "
"<emphasis>širine</emphasis> na zahtevo za spremembo velikosti. Običajno je "
"1x1. Druga okna pa, na primer terminalski emulatorji ali urejevalniki, "
"uporabljajo fiksne pisave in zahtevajo njihovo osnovno povečanje glede na "
"velikost enega znaka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Arrangement &amp; Access</title>"
msgstr "<title>Aranžma &amp; Dostop</title>"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keep above, Keep below"
msgstr "Zadrži zgoraj, zadrži spodaj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle whether to keep the window above/below all others."
msgstr "Preklopite, ali naj bo okno nad/pod vsemi drugimi."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autogroup with identical"
msgstr "Avtomatsko združi z identičnimi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle the grouping (commonly known as <emphasis>tabbing</emphasis>) of "
"windows."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite združevanje (splošno znano kot <emphasis>zavihki</emphasis>) oken."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autogroup in foreground"
msgstr "Avtomatsko združi v ospredju"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle whether to make the window active when it is added to the current "
"Autogroup."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite, ali naj bo okno aktivno, ko je dodano v trenutno samodejno "
"skupino."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autogroup by ID"
msgstr "Avtomatsko združi po ID-ju (identiteti)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a group via a user-defined ID. More than one rule can share the same "
"ID to allow for seemingly unrelated windows to be grouped."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite skupino prek uporabniško določenega ID-ja. Več kot eno pravilo "
"lahko deli isti ID, da omogoči združevanje na videz nepovezanih oken."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Skip taskbar"
msgstr "Preskoči opravilno vrstico"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle whether to display the window in the taskbar."
msgstr "Izberite, ali naj se okno prikaže v opravilni vrstici."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid "Skip pager"
msgstr "Preskoči pozivnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle whether to display the window in pager."
msgstr "Preklopite, ali naj se okno prikaže v pozivniku."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "Skip switcher"
msgstr "Preskoči menjalnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle whether to display the window in the <guilabel>ALT+TAB</guilabel> "
"list."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite, ali naj se okno prikaže na <guilabel>ALT+TAB</guilabel> seznamu."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut"
msgstr "Bližnjica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Assign a shortcut to the window. When <guilabel>Edit...</guilabel> is "
"clicked, additional instructions are presented."
msgstr ""
"Oknu dodelite bližnjico. Ko kliknete <guilabel>Uredi ...</guilabel>, se "
"prikažejo dodatna navodila."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Appearance &amp; Fixes</title>"
msgstr "<title>Videz &amp; Popravki</title>"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid "No titlebar and frame"
msgstr "Brez naslovne vrstice in okvirja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle whether to display the titlebar and frame around the window."
msgstr "Preklopite, ali želite prikazati naslovno vrstico in okvir okoli okna."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid "Titlebar color scheme"
msgstr "Barvna shema naslovne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:438
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select a color scheme for the titlebar of the window."
msgstr "Izberite barvno shemo za naslovno vrstico okna."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid "Active/Inactive opacity"
msgstr "Aktivna/neaktivna motnost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the window is active/inactive, set its opacity to the percentage "
"specified."
msgstr ""
"Ko je okno aktivno/neaktivno, nastavite njegovo motnost na določen odstotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Active/Inactive opacity</guilabel> can only be affected when "
"<guilabel>Desktop Effects</guilabel> are enabled."
msgstr ""
"Na <guilabel>Aktivno/neaktivno motnost</guilabel> lahko vplivate le, če so "
"omogočeni <guilabel>Učinki namizja</guilabel>."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid "Focus stealing prevention"
msgstr "Osredotočite se na preprečevanje kraje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a window wants focus, control on a scale (from <guilabel>None</"
"guilabel> to <guilabel>Extreme</guilabel>) whether to honor the request and "
"place above all other windows, or ignore its request (potentially leaving "
"the window behind other windows):"
msgstr ""
"Ko okno želi fokus, nastavite na lestvici (od <guilabel>Brez</guilabel> do "
"<guilabel>Ekstremno</guilabel>), ali želite izpolniti zahtevo in jo "
"postaviti nad vsa druga okna ali prezreti njeno zahtevo (potencialno pustite "
"okno za drugimi okni):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "None - Always grant focus to the window."
msgstr "Brez – vedno dodeli fokus oknu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Low</para>"
msgstr "<para>Nizko</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:456
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal"
msgstr "Nomalno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:457
#, no-c-format
msgid "High"
msgstr "Visoko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Extreme - The window's focus request is denied. Focus is only granted by "
"explicitly requesting via the mousing."
msgstr ""
"Ekstremno – zahteva za fokus okna je zavrnjena. Fokus je dodeljen le z "
"izrecno zahtevo prek miške."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <guilabel>Accept focus</guilabel> to make a window read-only - not "
"accept any keyboard input."
msgstr ""
"Glejte <guilabel>Sprejmi fokus</guilabel>, da naredite okno samo za branje - "
"ne sprejemajte nobenega vnosa s tipkovnice."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accept focus"
msgstr "Sprejmi fokus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle whether the window accepts keyboard input. Make the window read-only."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite, ali okno sprejema vnos s tipkovnico. Naredi okno samo za branje."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore global shortcuts"
msgstr "Ignorirajte globalne bližnjice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle whether to ignore global shortcuts (as defined by "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>System Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Shortcuts and "
"Gestures</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Global Shortcuts</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> or by running <varname>kcmshell6 keys</varname> in "
"<guilabel>konsole</guilabel>) while the window is active."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite med prezrtjem globalnih bližnjic (kot je določeno z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Sistemskimi nastavitvami</guimenu><guisubmenu>Bližnjice "
"in poteze</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Globalne bližnjice</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali z zagonom <varname >kcmshell6 keys</varname> v "
"<guilabel>konsole</guilabel>), medtem ko je okno aktivno."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closeable"
msgstr "Zaprljivo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle whether to display the <guilabel>Close</guilabel> button on the title "
"bar."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite, ali želite prikazati gumb <guilabel>Zapri</guilabel> v naslovni "
"vrstici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A terminal window may still be closed by the end user by ending the shell "
"session however using <guilabel>Accept focus</guilabel> to disable keyboard "
"input will make it more difficult to close the window."
msgstr ""
"Končni uporabnik lahko še vedno zapre okno terminala, če konča sejo ukazne "
"lupine, vendar bo uporaba <guilabel>Sprejmi fokus</guilabel> za onemogočanje "
"vnosa s tipkovnico otežila zapiranje okna."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis role=\"bold\">Window type</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis role=\"bold\">Vrsta okna</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Change the window to another type and inherit the characteristics of that "
"window:"
msgstr "Spremenite okno v drugo vrsto in podedujte značilnosti tega okna:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal Window"
msgstr "Normalo okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dialog Window"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid "Utility Window"
msgstr "Okno pripomočka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dock (panel)"
msgstr "Dok (plošča)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "Torn-Off Menu"
msgstr "Odtrgan meni (torn-off menu)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "Splash Screen"
msgstr "Zaslon ob zagonu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid "Desktop"
msgstr "Namizje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid "Standalone Menubar"
msgstr "Samostojna menijska vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "On Screen Display"
msgstr "Prikaz na zaslonu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use with care because unwanted results may be introduced. For example, a "
"<guilabel>Splash Screen</guilabel> is a automatically closed by &kwin; when "
"clicked."
msgstr ""
"Uporabljajte previdno, ker lahko pride do neželenih rezultatov. Na primer, "
"&kwin; samodejno zapre <guilabel>Začetni zaslon</guilabel> ob kliku."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid "Block compositing"
msgstr "Bločno sestavljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle whether to disable compositing while the window <emphasis>exists</"
"emphasis>. If compositing is enabled and the rule specifies to disable "
"compositing, while <emphasis>any</emphasis> matching window exists, "
"compositing will be disabled. Compositing is re-enabled when the last "
"matching window terminates."
msgstr ""
"Preklopite, ali želite onemogočiti sestavljanje, medtem ko okno "
"<emphasis>obstaja</emphasis>. Če je sestavljanje omogočeno in pravilo določa "
"onemogočanje sestavljanja, medtem ko obstaja <emphasis>katero koli</"
"emphasis> ustrezno okno, bo sestavljanje onemogočeno. Sestavljanje je znova "
"omogočeno, ko se zapre zadnje okno, ujemajoče s staro nastavitvijo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:517
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "Primeri"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first example details all the necessary steps to create the rules. In "
"order to keep this page a manageable size, subsequent examples only list "
"steps specific to the example."
msgstr ""
"Prvi primer podrobno opisuje vse potrebne korake za ustvarjanje pravil. Da "
"bi ta stran ohranila obvladljivo velikost, naslednji primeri navajajo le "
"korake, specifične za primer."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Pager</guilabel> attribute refers to the <guilabel>Virtual "
"Desktop Manager</guilabel>:"
msgstr ""
"Atribut <guilabel>Pozivnik</guilabel> se nanaša na <guilabel>Upravljalnik "
"virtualnega namizja</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pin a Window to a Desktop and set other Attributes"
msgstr "Pripnite okno na namizje in nastavite druge atribute"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pin &akregator; to <emphasis>Virtual Desktop 2</emphasis>. Additionally, "
"start the application with a preferred size and position. For each "
"attribute, use the <guilabel>Apply Initially</guilabel> <link linkend="
"\"parameters\">parameter</link> so it can be overridden at run-time."
msgstr ""
"Pripnite &akregator; na <emphasis>Virtualno namizje 2</emphasis>. Poleg tega "
"zaženite aplikacijo z želeno velikostjo in položajem. Za vsak atribut "
"uporabite <link linkend=\"parameters\">parameter</link> <guilabel>Uporabi na "
"začetku</guilabel>, da ga je mogoče preglasiti med izvajanjem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kwin; rule is created as follows:"
msgstr "&kwin; pravilo je ustvarjeno na naslednji način:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start &akregator; on <emphasis>desktop two</emphasis>, size and position it "
"to suit:"
msgstr ""
"Zaženi &akregator; na <emphasis>namizju dve</emphasis>, v velikosti in na "
"mestu, da ustreza:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right-click on the titlebar and select <menuchoice><guimenu>More Actions</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Window Manager Settings...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>:"
msgstr ""
"Z desno miškino tipko kliknite naslovno vrstico in izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Več dejanj</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nastavitve upravitelja "
"oken ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>Window Rules</guilabel> in the left column and click on "
"<guilabel>New...</guilabel>:"
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Okenska pravila</guilabel> v levem stolpcu in kliknite "
"<guilabel>Novo...</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Edit Window-Specific Settings</guilabel> window is displayed. "
"<guilabel>Window matching</guilabel> is the default tab:"
msgstr ""
"Prikaže se okno <guilabel>Urejanje nastavitev, specifičnih za okno</"
"guilabel>. <guilabel>Ujemanje oken</guilabel> je privzeti zavihek:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> with <guilabel>0s delay</"
"guilabel> the cursor immediately turns into cross-hairs. Click (anywhere) "
"inside the &akregator; window (but not the title bar). The window criteria "
"are presented. Match only by primary class name so leave the check boxes "
"unchecked - for additional information see <link linkend=\"window-matching"
"\">window matching</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Kliknite <guilabel>Zaznaj lastnosti okna</guilabel> z <guilabel>zakasnitvijo "
"0s</guilabel>, kazalec se takoj spremeni v križec. Kliknite (kamor koli) "
"znotraj &akregator; okna (vendar ne naslovne vrstice). Predstavljeni so "
"kriteriji okna. Ujemanje je samo z imenom primarnega razreda, zato pustite "
"potrditvena polja nepotrjena - za dodatne informacije glejte <link linkend="
"\"window-matching\">ujemanje oken</link>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:599
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking <guilabel>OK</guilabel> the previous window back-fills the results "
"in the <guilabel>Window Matching</guilabel> tab. Enter a meaningful text in "
"the <guilabel>Description</guilabel> field (which is displayed in the "
"<guilabel>KWin Rule</guilabel> window):"
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete <guilabel>V redu</guilabel>, prejšnje okno zapolni rezultate v "
"zavihku <guilabel>Ujemanje oken</guilabel>. Vnesite smiselno besedilo v "
"polje <guilabel>Opis</guilabel> (ki je prikazano v oknu <guilabel>KWin "
"Pravilo</guilabel>):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable the window attributes: <guilabel>Position</guilabel>, <guilabel>Size</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Desktop</guilabel>. The initial values are set by "
"<guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> and can be overridden:"
msgstr ""
"Omogočite atribute okna: <guilabel>Položaj</guilabel>, <guilabel>Velikost</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Namizje</guilabel>. Začetne vrednosti so nastavljene "
"v <guilabel>Zaznaj lastnosti okna</guilabel> in jih je mogoče preglasiti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking <guilabel>OK</guilabel> in the previous window returns to the main "
"<guilabel>KWin Rules</guilabel>. The new rule with its description is listed:"
msgstr ""
"Če v prejšnjem oknu kliknete <guilabel>V redu</guilabel>, se vrnete na "
"glavna <guilabel>Pravila KWin</guilabel>. Navedeno je novo pravilo z "
"njegovim opisom:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click <guilabel>OK</guilabel> to close the window."
msgstr "Kliknite <guilabel>V redu</guilabel>, da zaprete okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid "Done."
msgstr "Končano."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application on all Desktops and Handle One Child Window Uniquely"
msgstr ""
"Uporaba na vseh namizjih in enolično upravljanje z enim podrejenim oknom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:640
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Except for conversation windows, display &kopete; and its children windows "
"on all desktops and skip the systray and pager. For children conversation "
"windows, treat them as the parent window except show them in systray."
msgstr ""
"Razen oken za pogovore prikažite &kopete; in njegova podrejena okna na vseh "
"namizjih ter preskočite sistemski prikazovalnik in pozivnik. Podrejena "
"pogovorna okna obravnavajte kot matično okno, razen da jih prikaži v "
"sistemskem oknu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each attribute, use the <guilabel>Force</guilabel> <link linkend="
"\"parameters\">parameter</link> so it can not be overridden."
msgstr ""
"Za vsak atribut uporabite <link linkend=\"parameters\">parameter</link> "
"<guilabel>Prislila</guilabel>, da ga ni mogoče prepisati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:644
#, no-c-format
msgid "In order to implement the above, two rules need to be created:"
msgstr "Za izvajanje zgoraj navedenega je treba ustvariti dve pravili:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:647
#, no-c-format
msgid "A rule for <guilabel>Kopete Chat</guilabel> and"
msgstr "Pravilo za <guilabel>Kopete Chat</guilabel> in"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid "A rule for &kopete;"
msgstr "Pravilo za &kopete;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:650
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Kopete Chat</guilabel> rule's matching-criteria is more "
"restrictive than the <emphasis>Kopete</emphasis> rule as it needs to match a "
"specific Window Role: the chat window. Due to <link linkend=\"rule-evaluation"
"\">rule evaluation</link> processing, the <guilabel>Kopete Chat</guilabel> "
"rule must precede the &kopete; rule in the <link linkend=\"kopete-kwin-rule-"
"list\">KWin Rule list for Kopete</link>."
msgstr ""
"Kriteriji ujemanja pravila <guilabel>Klepet Kopete</guilabel> so bolj "
"restriktivni kot pravilo <emphasis>Kopete</emphasis>, saj se morajo ujemati "
"z določeno vlogo okna: oknom za klepet. Zaradi <link linkend=\"rule-"
"evaluation\">ocenjevanja pravil</link> obdelave mora biti pravilo "
"<guilabel>kelepeta Kopete</guilabel> pred pravilom &kopete; pravilo na <link "
"linkend=\"kopete-kwin-rule-list\">seznamu pravil KWin za Kopete</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kopete Chat Rule"
msgstr "Pravilo klepeta Kopete"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:653
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assuming a <guilabel>Kopete Chat</guilabel> window is open:"
msgstr "Ob predpostavki, da je odprto okno <guilabel>Klepet Kopete</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:656
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> and select the "
"<guilabel>Kopete Chat</guilabel> window. Check the <guilabel>Window role</"
"guilabel> box to restrict the criteria to chat windows - for additional "
"information see <link linkend=\"window-matching\">window matching</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <guilabel>Zaznaj lastnosti okna</guilabel> in izberite okno "
"<guilabel>Klepet Kopete</guilabel>. Označite polje <guilabel>Vloga okna</"
"guilabel>, da omejite merila za okna za klepet - za dodatne informacije "
"glejte <link linkend=\"window-matching\">ujemanje oken</link>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:668 index.docbook:713 index.docbook:774 index.docbook:842
#: index.docbook:885 index.docbook:928
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking <guilabel>OK</guilabel> in the previous window back-fills the "
"results in the <guilabel>Window Matching</guilabel> tab. Enter a meaningful "
"text in the <guilabel>Description</guilabel> box:"
msgstr ""
"Klik na <guilabel>V redu</guilabel> v prejšnjem oknu zapolni rezultate v "
"zavihku <guilabel>Ujemanje oken</guilabel>. Vnesite smiselno besedilo v "
"polje <guilabel>Opis</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:680 index.docbook:725 index.docbook:854 index.docbook:897
#: index.docbook:940
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable the following attributes:"
msgstr "Omogočite naslednje atribute:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:692 index.docbook:737 index.docbook:798 index.docbook:866
#: index.docbook:909 index.docbook:952 index.docbook:1005
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click through to complete entry of the rule."
msgstr "Kliknite za dokončanje vnosa pravila."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:694
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Skip taskbar</guilabel> attribute is set to <guilabel>No</"
"guilabel> to display the window in the taskbar which loosely translates to: "
"<emphasis>no</emphasis> <emphasis>do not</emphasis> <emphasis>skip taskbar</"
"emphasis> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Face-smile."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>."
msgstr ""
"Atribut <guilabel>Preskoči opravilno vrstico</guilabel> je nastavljen na "
"<guilabel>Ne</guilabel>, da prikaže okno v opravilni vrstici, kar v splošnem "
"pomeni: <emphasis>ne</emphasis > <emphasis>preskoči opravilne vrstico</"
"emphasis> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"Face-smile."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:697
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kopete Rule"
msgstr "Pravilo Kopete"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assuming &kopete; is open:"
msgstr "Ob predpostavki, da je &kopete; odprt:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:701
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> and select the &kopete; "
"window. Match only by primary class name so leave the check boxes unchecked "
"- for additional information see <link linkend=\"window-matching\">window "
"matching</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <guilabel>Zaznaj lastnosti okna</guilabel> in izberite datoteko "
"&kopete; okno. Ujemanje je samo z imenom primarnega razreda, zato pustite "
"potrditvena polja nepotrjena - za dodatne informacije glejte <link linkend="
"\"window-matching\">ujemanje oken</link>:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kopete KWin Rule List"
msgstr "Seznam pravil Kopete KWin"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:741
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As mentioned, due to <link linkend=\"rule-evaluation\">rule evaluation</"
"link> processing, the <guilabel>Kopete Chat</guilabel> rule must precede the "
"&kopete; rule:"
msgstr ""
"Kot že omenjeno, mora zaradi <link linkend=\"rule-evaluation\">ocenjevanja "
"pravil</link> obdelave pravilo <guilabel>Kopete Chat</guilabel> biti pred "
"pravilom &kopete;:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid "Suppress a Window from showing on Pager"
msgstr "Prepreči, da se okno pojavi na pozivniku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:757
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>KNotes</guilabel> currently does not allow for its notes to skip "
"the pager however a rule easily solves this shortcoming."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>KNotes</guilabel> trenutno ne dovoljuje, da bi njegovi zapiski "
"preskočili pozivnik, vendar pravilo enostavno odpravi to pomanjkljivost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:759
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assuming a <emphasis>sticky note</emphasis>' window is available:"
msgstr ""
"Ob predpostavki, da je na voljo okno s <emphasis>samolepljivim listkom</"
"emphasis>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> and select any "
"<emphasis>sticky note</emphasis> window. Match only by primary class name so "
"leave the check boxes unchecked - for additional information see <link "
"linkend=\"window-matching\">window matching</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <guilabel>Zaznaj lastnosti okna</guilabel> in izberite poljubno "
"okno <emphasis>samolepilnega listka</emphasis>. Ujemanje je samo z imenom "
"primarnega razreda, zato pustite potrditvena polja nepotrjena - za dodatne "
"informacije glejte <link linkend=\"window-matching\">ujemanje oken</link>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:786
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable the <guilabel>Skip Pager</guilabel> attribute with the "
"<guilabel>Force</guilabel> <link linkend=\"parameters\">parameter</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Omogočite atribut <guilabel>Preskoči pozivnik </guilabel> s "
"<guilabel>Prisila</guilabel> <link linkend=\"parameters\">parametrom</link>:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:801
#, no-c-format
msgid "Force a Window to the Top"
msgstr "Vsili okno na vrh"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:802
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To pop an active window to the top, set its <guilabel>Focus stealing "
"prevention</guilabel> attribute to <guilabel>None</guilabel>, typically, in "
"conjunction with the <guilabel>Force</guilabel> <link linkend=\"parameters"
"\">parameter</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite aktivno okno prikazati na vrhu, nastavite njegov atribut "
"<guilabel>Preprečevanje kraje fokusa</guilabel> na <guilabel>Brez</"
"guilabel>, običajno v povezavi s <link linkend=\"parameters\">parametrom</"
"link> <guilabel>Prisila</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:816
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multiple Rules per Application"
msgstr "Več pravil na posamezno uporabo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<application>Thunderbird</application> has several different child windows. "
"This example:"
msgstr ""
"<application>Thunderbird</application> ima več različnih podrejenih oken. Ta "
"primer:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:820
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pin <application>Thunderbird</application>'s main window on "
"<emphasis>Virtual Desktop 1</emphasis> with a specific size and location on "
"the desktop."
msgstr ""
"Pripnite glavno okno <application>Thunderbird</application> na "
"<emphasis>Virtualno Namizje 1</emphasis> z določeno velikostjo in mestom na "
"namizju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:821
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allow the <application>Thunderbird</application> composer window to reside "
"on any desktop and when activated, force focus and pop it to the top of all "
"windows."
msgstr ""
"Dovolite, da se okno skladatelja <application>Thunderbird</application> "
"nahaja na poljubnem namizju in ko je aktivirano, prisilite fokus in ga "
"pomaknite na vrh vseh oken."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:822
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pop the <application>Thunderbird</application> reminder to the top and do "
"not give it focus so it isn't inadvertently dismissed."
msgstr ""
"Postavite opomnik <application>Thunderbird</application> na vrh in ga ne "
"usmerite v fokus, da ga ne zavržete nehote."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:824
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each rule's matching criteria is sufficiently restrictive so their order "
"within the main &kwin; window is not important to affect <link linkend="
"\"rule-evaluation\">rule evaluation</link>."
msgstr ""
"Kriteriji ujemanja vsakega pravila so dovolj restriktivni, tako da njihov "
"vrstni red znotraj glavnega &kwin; okna ni pomemben in ne vplivana na <link "
"linkend=\"rule-evaluation\">vrednotenje pravil</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:826
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thunderbird - Main"
msgstr "Thunderbird - Glavno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:827
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Assuming the <guilabel>Thunderbird Main</guilabel> window is open, sized and "
"position to suit:"
msgstr ""
"Ob predpostavki, da je <guilabel>glavno okno Thunderbird</guilabel> odprto, "
"velikost in položaj ustrezajo:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> and select the "
"<guilabel>Thunderbird Main</guilabel> window. Check the <guilabel>Window "
"role</guilabel> box to restrict the criteria to the main window - for "
"additional information see <link linkend=\"window-matching\">window "
"matching</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <guilabel>Zaznaj lastnosti okna</guilabel> in izberite "
"<guilabel>Glavno okno Thunderbird</guilabel>. Označite polje <guilabel>Vloga "
"okna</guilabel>, da omejite merila za glavno okno - za dodatne informacije "
"glejte <link linkend=\"window-matching\">ujemanje oken</link>:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:869
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thunderbird - Composer"
msgstr "Thunderbird - skladatelj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:870
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assuming a <guilabel>Thunderbird Composer</guilabel> window is open:"
msgstr ""
"Ob predpostavki, da je odprto okno <guilabel>Thunderbird skladatelj</"
"guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:873
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> and select the "
"<guilabel>Thunderbird Compose</guilabel> window. Check the <guilabel>Window "
"role</guilabel> and <guilabel>Window type</guilabel> boxes to restrict the "
"criteria to composition windows - for additional information see <link "
"linkend=\"window-matching\">window matching</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <guilabel>Zaznaj lastnosti okna</guilabel> in izberite okno "
"<guilabel>Thunderbird skladatelj</guilabel>. Označite polji <guilabel>Vloga "
"okna</guilabel> in <guilabel>Vrsta okna</guilabel>, da omejite merila na "
"okna sestave - za dodatne informacije glejte <link linkend=\"window-matching"
"\">ujemanje oken</link> :"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:912
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thunderbird - Reminder"
msgstr "Thunderbird - opomnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:913
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assuming a <guilabel>Thunderbird Reminder</guilabel> window is open:"
msgstr ""
"Ob predpostavki, da je odprto okno <guilabel>Thunderbird opomnik</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:916
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> and select the "
"<guilabel>Thunderbird Reminder</guilabel> window. Check the "
"<guilabel>Secondary class name</guilabel> and <guilabel>Window Type</"
"guilabel> boxes to restrict the criteria to reminder windows - for "
"additional information see <link linkend=\"window-matching\">window "
"matching</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <guilabel>Zaznaj lastnosti okna</guilabel> in izberite okno "
"<guilabel>Opomnik Thunderbird</guilabel>. Označite polja <guilabel>Ime "
"sekundarnega razreda</guilabel> in <guilabel>Vrsta okna</guilabel>, da "
"omejite merila na okna opomnikov - za dodatne informacije glejte <link "
"linkend=\"window-matching\">ujemanje oken</link >:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:958
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Workarounds"
msgstr "Obhod uporabe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid "Below are Workarounds for misbehaving applications."
msgstr "Spodaj so rešitve za nepravilno delujoče aplikacije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:961
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are unfamiliar with creating &kwin; Rules, see this <link linkend="
"\"pin-a-window-to-a-desktop-and-set-other-attributes\">detailed example</"
"link> to base your new rule."
msgstr ""
"Če niste seznanjeni z ustvarjanjem &kwin; Pravili, glejte ta <link linkend="
"\"pin-a-window-to-a-desktop-and-set-other-attributes\">podroben primer</"
"link>, ki bo podlaga za vaše novo pravilo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:963
#, no-c-format
msgid "Full-screen Re-size Error"
msgstr "Napaka pri spreminjanju velikosti celotnega zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:964
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&Emacs; and <guilabel>gVim</guilabel>, when maximized (full-screen mode) and "
"under certain conditions may encounter window re-sizing issues - see <ulink "
"url=\"https://bugs.kde.org/show_bug.cgi?id=252314\">Emacs window resizes ..."
"</ulink> A &kwin; Rule will work-around the issue."
msgstr ""
"&Emacs; in <guilabel>gVim</guilabel>, ko je maksimiziran (celozaslonski "
"način) in pod določenimi pogoji lahko, naleti na težave pri spreminjanju "
"velikosti oken - glejte <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org/show_bug.cgi? "
"id=252314\">Emacs okno spremeni velikost ...</ulink> A &kwin; Pravilo bo "
"rešilo težavo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:966
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assuming an &Emacs; window is open:"
msgstr "Ob predpostavki, da je &Emacs; okno odprto:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:969
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guilabel>Detect Window Properties</guilabel> and select the &Emacs; "
"window. Match only by <guilabel>primary class name</guilabel> so leave the "
"check boxes unchecked - for additional information see <link linkend="
"\"window-matching\">window matching</link>"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <guilabel>Zaznaj lastnosti okna</guilabel> in izberite &Emacs; "
"okno. Ujemanje je samo po <guilabel>imenu primarnega razreda</guilabel>, "
"zato pustite potrditvena polja nepotrjena - za dodatne informacije glejte "
"<link linkend=\"window-matching\">ujemanje oken</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:981
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking <guilabel>OK</guilabel> in the previous window back-fills the "
"results in the <guilabel>Window Matching</guilabel> tab. Enter a meaningful "
"text in the <guilabel>Description</guilabel> text box:"
msgstr ""
"Klik na <guilabel>V redu</guilabel> v prejšnjem oknu zapolni rezultate v "
"zavihku <guilabel>Ujemanje oken</guilabel>. V besedilno polje "
"<guilabel>Opis</guilabel> vnesite smiselno besedilo:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:993
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ignore &Emacs;'s full-screen request by enabling the <guilabel>Obey geometry "
"restrictions</guilabel> attribute, toggling it to off (<guilabel>No</"
"guilabel>) to ignore and selecting the <guilabel>Force</guilabel> <link "
"linkend=\"parameters\">parameter</link>:"
msgstr ""
"Ignorirajte celozaslonsko zahtevo &Emacs; tako, da omogočite atribut "
"<guilabel>Upoštevaj geometrijske omejitve</guilabel>, ga preklopite na "
"izklopljeno (<guilabel>Ne</guilabel>), da prezrete, in izberete <link "
"linkend=\"parameters\">parameter</link> <guilabel>Prisili</guilabel >:"

